ory>\n                        \u003Corigin>\n                            \u003CorigPlace>\n                                \u003CplaceName type=\"ancient\" ref=\"http://pleiades.stoa.org/places/462378\">Mutyca\u003C/placeName>\t\t\n                                \u003CplaceName type=\"modern\" ref=\"http://sws.geonames.org/6541972\">Modica\u003C/placeName>\n                            \t\u003Cgeo>36.84594, 14.77399\u003C/geo>\n\t\t\u003C/origPlace>\n                            \u003CorigDate datingMethod=\"#julian\" notBefore-custom=\"0301\" notAfter-custom=\"0500\">late Roman imperial\u003C/origDate>\n                        \u003C/origin>\n                        \u003Cprovenance type=\"found\" subtype=\"discovered\">Chance find of a hypogeum in contrada Rocciola-Scrofani (Cozzo Rotondo), eastern side of Modica\u003Cgeo>36.8417895,14.7706654\u003C/geo>, subsequently built over, from which remains this epigraphic fragment\u003C/provenance>\u003C!-- approx location of contrada Rocciola / noted archaeological site -->\n                        \u003Cprovenance type=\"observed\" subtype=\"autopsied\">None\u003C/provenance>\n                        \u003Cacquisition/>\n                    \u003C/history>\n                \u003C/msDesc>\n            \u003C/sourceDesc>\n        \u003C/fileDesc>\n        \u003CencodingDesc>\n             \u003Cp>Encoded following the latest EpiDoc guidelines\u003C/p>\n             \u003Cxi:include href=\"../alists/ISicily-taxonomies.xml\">\n                 \u003Cxi:fallback>\n                     \u003Cp>Taxonomies for ISicily controlled values\u003C/p>\n                 \u003C/xi:fallback>\n             \u003C/xi:include>\n\t  \u003Cxi:include href=\"../alists/charDecl.xml\">\n\t     \u003Cxi:fallback>\n\t       \u003Cp>ISicily glyphs authority list\u003C/p>\n\t     \u003C/xi:fallback>\n\t   \u003C/xi:include>\n         \u003C/encodingDesc>\n        \u003CprofileDesc>\n            \u003CcalendarDesc>\n                \u003Ccalendar xml: